nta.system: // List one or more processes to be composed into a system. system Controller, Pump, Machine, Fluctuation, AccumulatedVolume, SafetyMonitor;

query.formula: strategy LowVolume2 = minE (aov) [<=120] {} -> {t, v, p, l}: <> elapsed >= 120
strategy SmartSwitching = minE (aov/120 + switches/2) [<=120] {p} -> {t, v}: <> elapsed >= 120
